Usage: attachDiode [-help] -diodeCell <cellName> -pin {instName termName}
                   [-prefix <prefixName>] [-loc {locX locY} [-orient <orient>]]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-diodeCell <cellName>     # Specifies the name of the diode cell master.
                          # (string, required)
-loc {locX locY}          # Specifies the location of the lower left corner of
                          # the diode. (string, optional)
-orient <orient>          # Specifies orientation of the placed diode.
                          # (string, optional)
-pin {instName termName}  # Specifies the pin associated with the diode.
                          # (string, required)
-prefix <prefixName>      # Specifies the prefix name of the diode cell
                          # instances. (string, optional)